<h2>Help</h2>
<p>Welcome to the Training Sesh help page. Here’s how you can use the system:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Create a Booking:</strong> Go to the "Create Booking" page and fill in the required details.</li>
  <li><strong>View Bookings:</strong> Click on "View Bookings" to see all your training sessions.</li>
  <li><strong>Edit a Booking:</strong> Select a session from the list and click "Edit" to update details.</li>
  <li><strong>Delete a Booking:</strong> Click "Delete" next to a session to remove it.</li>
  <li><strong>Generate Report:</strong> Enter the user’s name and date range in the "Report" section to view a summary of sessions.</li>
  <li><strong>Contact Support:</strong> If you need further assistance, please email us at support@trainingsesh.com.</li>
</ul>

